			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Gal in nakpitakin Saul neh a, gal thaltawite in nakpitakin amah liamsak hi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Tua ciangin Saul in a galhiam puapa kiangah, “Hih dawibia mite hong pai-in kei hong dawtletin hong mawlpih kha ding uh ahih manin na namsau dok inla, tua tawh hong dawtlet in,” a ci hi. Ahih hangin a galhiam puapa in hih ngam lo hi; bang hang hiam cih leh amah lau mahmah hi. Tua ahih ciangin Saul in ama namsau la-in tua tungah puk hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> A galhiam puapa in Saul a sihna a muh ciangin amah zong a namsau tungah kipuksuk sakin amah tawh a sikhawm hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Tua bangin Saul, a tapa thumte, a galhiam puapa, le a mi khempeuh, a ni kikhatin a sikhawm uh hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Tua ciangin Jezreel kuam galkhat le Jordan galkhat a om Israel mite in Israel mite tai-in Saul le a tapate a sih khitna thu a zak uh ciangin amaute in a khuapite uh nusia-in tai uh ahih ciangin Filistia-te hong pai-in tuate sungah a teng uh hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> A zing ciangin a kithat mite’ na a la dingin Filistia-te hong pai ciangin Saul le a tapa thumte Gilboa Mual tungah a si mu uh hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Amaute in Saul’ lu tankhia-in a galhiam hawkkhia uh a, a milimte uh le mite kiangah hih thuhoih a puak dingin Filistia gam sung khempeuhah kamtaite a sawl uh hi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Amaute in Ashtaroth biakinn sungah ama galhiam koih uh a, Bethshan khuakulhah ama luang a suang uh hi.",
